  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to DeviceKit-disks</title>

    <para>The <application>DeviceKit-disks</application> package is a daemon
    that provide interfaces to obtain information and perform operations on
    storage devices.</para>

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
